## Status Values

- `available` - Item is available for rental
- `rented_out` - Item is currently rented out
- `in_maintenance` - Item is under maintenance

## Rental Period Values

- `hourly` - Hourly rental
- `daily` - Daily rental
- `weekly` - Weekly rental
- `monthly` - Monthly rental

